*ಕಲಾಶೃಂಗಾರ* 🌸

We shot it on my neighbor’s terrace, and I’m absolutely loving the final video and my look. Huge thanks to @makeupby_plavanya for the amazing makeup and @yesh1th_portraits for capturing the video so perfectly!
🖤 Mood: Doing my own thing. Always
